================================================================================
Open Core Strategy
================================================================================

ALICE-Zip uses an Open Core licensing model:

| Product              | License        | Description                          |
|----------------------|----------------|--------------------------------------|
| ALICE Core (libalice)| MIT            | Free and open source                 |
| ALICE Optimizer      | Commercial     | Subscription-based                   |
| ALICE Enterprise     | Commercial     | Annual contract                      |

