================================================================================
PART 3: Game Industry Exception
================================================================================

As a token of gratitude to the game industry, the following exception applies:

ELIGIBLE USES (Attribution Only - No License Fee Required)
----------------------------------------------------------
The following game development uses are granted a royalty-free license with
attribution only:

- Mobile games (iOS, Android, etc.)
- Console games (PlayStation, Xbox, Nintendo Switch, etc.)
- PC games (Steam, Epic Games Store, GOG, etc.)
- Arcade games
- VR games / AR games
- Online games (MMORPG, FPS, TPS, fighting games, etc.)
- Browser games
- Serious games / Educational games

ATTRIBUTION REQUIREMENT
-----------------------
Display the following attribution in your game's credits screen or About section:

  "Powered by ALICE-Zip (https://github.com/ext-sakamoro/ALICE-Zip)"

NON-ELIGIBLE USES (Commercial License Required)
-----------------------------------------------
The following uses are NOT covered by this exception and require a commercial
license:

- Game console firmware / OS integration (PlayStation, Xbox, Nintendo, etc.)
- Game engines / Middleware integration (Unity, Unreal Engine, etc.)
- VTuber / Streaming related tools
- Metaverse platforms
- Casino / Gambling applications
- Pachinko / Pachislot machines
- Social casino games
- Esports management / streaming platforms
- Game streaming support tools

================================================================================
Summary
================================================================================

| Use Case                        | Core (Free) | Pro        | Enterprise  |
|---------------------------------|-------------|------------|-------------|
| Personal / Educational          | MIT         | -          | -           |
| Game Development (see Part 3)   | MIT + Attr  | Free*      | -           |
| Commercial (small scale)        | MIT         | Optional   | -           |
| Commercial (optimization needs) | MIT         | Required   | -           |
| Enterprise / Data Center        | MIT         | -          | Required    |

* Game Industry Exception: Pro features are also free with attribution for
  eligible game development uses (see Part 3).

The Core library (libalice) is always FREE under MIT license.
Pro and Enterprise products provide additional value for professional use.

